        "en": "I just wanted to support Erika because you're working so hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri007.m4a",
      "text": "それが上から目線だって言ってるの。ちょっと人気が\n出たからって調子に乗って、ウザいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds condescending. Just because you're a bit popular‚\ndoesn't mean you can act all high and mighty. It's annoying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "上から目線だなんて、そんなつもりは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never intended to sound condescending…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri008.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは気楽でいいよね。フリフリの衣装を着て\n適当に媚び売れば周りがちやほやしてくれるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being an idol must be easy. Wear flashy outfits‚\nact cute‚ and everyone fawns over you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 210.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "……それは違うわ\n私は媚びを売ったことなんて一度も無い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true…\nI've never acted cute just for attention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri009.m4a",
      "text": "よく言うわね。さっきの「私達、サニーピースです」\nってやつ、めっちゃウケたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have the nerve.\nSaying \"We are Sunny Peace\" earlier was laughable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri010.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとよくやるよね～\n私にはとても真似出来そうにないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's truly impressive.\nSomething I couldn't possibly mimic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "よく知りもせずに、アイドルを馬鹿にしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't mock idols when you don't even understand them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri011.m4a",
      "text": "馬鹿になんかしてないわ。ダンサーよりアイドルの方が\n人気者になれるし、お金も儲かるものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not mocking. It's just that\nidols are more popular and earn more money than dancers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri012.m4a",
      "text": "怜がダンサーを辞めてアイドルに鞍替えした気持ち\nよーく分かるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I completely \"understand\"\nwhy Rei switched from being a dancer to an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 247.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "私はそんな理由でアイドルになった訳じゃない\nあのままダンスを続けても認めてもらえないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not the reason I became an idol.\nI felt unappreciated as a dancer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri013.m4a",
      "text": "ようするに、ダンサーを続けるのがキツくなったから\nアイドルに逃げたんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ you ran to being an idol\nbecause being a dancer became too hard‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 261.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri014.m4a",
      "text": "私は逃げなかった。私は血の滲むような努力をして\nダンサーとして成功を掴んだのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't run away. I worked tirelessly\nand achieved success as a dancer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri015.m4a",
      "text": "ヘラヘラ笑って媚びを売ってるだけの\nあんたとは違うのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike you‚\nwho just smiles and acts cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 272.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
