      "text": "私達が努力していないって言うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying we don't work hard?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri016.m4a",
      "text": "事実でしょ\nサニーピースなんて、大した実力もないくせに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the truth.\nSunny Peace isn't even that talented.",
        "id": ""
      },
