    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 287.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "そのまま口論になって\nエリカと喧嘩別れになったんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It ended up turning into an argument.\nI left after having a fight with Erika…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことがあったのか……\n彼女の言ったことはあまり気にしない方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's what happened…\nDon't let her words get to you too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 300.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜が誰よりも努力していることは\nみんな分かっているから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone knows\nhow hard you're working‚ more than anyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。でも、エリカだって\nダンサーとして必死に努力してきたはずなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But Erika has also\nbeen working desperately as a dancer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 312.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "同じように努力して頑張ってるアイドルを\n馬鹿にするなんて悔しくて、腹が立って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's frustrating that she belittles idols\nwho are working just as hard. I was so angry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
